Package it.bancaditalia.oss.vtl.util

Class Utils

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.bancaditalia.oss.vtl.util.Utils
  • public final class Utils
extends Object
    This class contains various utility functions used by the VTL Engine implementation. Most of the functions are wrappers of the standard packages in Java 8.
    Author:
    Valentino Pinna
    See Also:
